  "title": "More Buckets",
  "description": "Adds a bunch of useful buckets for different materials!",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://v.blakesmods.com/banners/morebuckets?source=modrinth\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cucumber\"><img src=\"https://blakesmods.com/img/banner/cucumber_required.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"display: flex;\" align=\"left\"><a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/more-buckets\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/morebuckets/downloads&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/more-buckets\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/morebuckets/version&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/more-buckets\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/morebuckets/mc_version&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a href=\"https://blakesmods.com/wiki/morebuckets\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=wiki&amp;message=view&amp;color=brightgreen&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">More Buckets adds more Buckets which can be used to transfer larger quantities of fluid.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Features</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Adds buckets for more materials that can hold greater amounts of fluid.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Buckets work as fluid tanks and are compatible with most fluid insertion/extraction machines.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Buckets can be used in crafting recipes for more efficient crafting.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7UGSMzy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"648\" height=\"218\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Credits</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod was inspired by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/mapping-and-modding-java-edition/minecraft-mods/1285785-1-6-2-forge-diamond-buckets-v0-98d-hold-more\">Diamond Buckets+</a>.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/blakesmods\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/fdf1b29a-987b-450e-b6d4-a16c2da8aadf.png\" width=\"1086\" height=\"170\"></strong></a></span></p>",
